===========================================================================

PREAMBLE

This license governs the QODER_FREERUNNER enhancement system, which represents
a significant architectural evolution of the Qoder agentic coding platform.
The system integrates AI-SIEM security monitoring with BMAD-METHOD agile
development, creating a unified pre-integrated environment with operation
intercept modifiers and cloud storage runtime capabilities.

This work is a joint program between the primary creator (JlovesYouGit) and
the Alibaba WebSearch Qoder creators, building upon the foundational Qoder
platform technology while introducing revolutionary enhancements.

===========================================================================

DEFINITIONS

"QODER_FREERUNNER" - The enhanced pre-integrated system comprising:
- AI-SIEM + BMAD-METHOD unified integration
- Operation intercept modifiers for cloud storage runtime
- Unified MCP integration with cross-module capabilities
- Runtime capability detection and behavior adaptation
- Pre-configured workflows and autonomous execution

"Core Platform" - The original Alibaba WebSearch Qoder agentic coding platform
including its base architecture, agentic features, and core AI capabilities.

"Enhancements" - All architectural improvements, integrations, and novel
functionalities introduced by the primary creator that extend beyond the
Core Platform capabilities.

